'''布莱斯村庄'''（Blaise Hamlet）是英格兰[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]北部亨伯里区的九间小屋，环绕一片绿地。所有的小屋，和绿地上的日晷，均被列为 I级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]。[[尼古拉斯·佩夫斯纳|尼古拉斯·佩夫斯纳]]将其描述为“风景如画的布局和设计”。<ref>{{NHLE|desc=Blaise Castle and Hamlet|num=1001426|accessdate=8 August 2016}}</ref>

布莱斯村庄建于1811年，为[[贵格会|贵格会]]教徒、[[银行家|银行家]]和慈善家、[[布莱斯城堡庄园|布莱斯城堡庄园]]主人约翰·斯坎德雷特·哈福德的退休员工建造，<ref name=nthist>{{cite web|title=The history of Blaise Hamlet|url=https://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/blaise-hamlet/features/the-history-of-blaise-hamlet|publisher=National Trust|access-date=8 August 2016|archive-date=2016-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712002418/http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/blaise-hamlet/features/the-history-of-blaise-hamlet|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[约翰·纳西|约翰·纳西]]设计，是第一个完全实现的[[田园城市理论|花园郊区]]，并奠定了几乎所有花园郊区的路线图。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Stern|first1=Robert A.M.|last2=Fishman|first2=David|last3=Tilove|first3=Jacob|title=Paradise Planned: The Garden Suburb and the Modern City|date=2013|publisher=The Monacelli Press|isbn=978-1580933261|page=23}}</ref> 这些小屋都是独一无二的，拥有砖砌烟囱和[[老虎窗|老虎窗]]。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Wilson|first1=Vicky|title=Photograph of the Circular Cottage, Blaise Hamlet, Bristol 1973|url=https://www.architecture.com/Explore/Revealingthecollections/CircularCottageBlaiseHamlet1973.aspx|publisher=Architecture.com|access-date=8 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818233042/https://www.architecture.com/Explore/Revealingthecollections/CircularCottageBlaiseHamlet1973.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它们是1782年由威廉·吉尔平牧师提倡的英国如画(picturesque)[[美学|美学]]理想的例子。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Willes|first1=Margaret|title=The Gardens of the British Working Class|date=2014|publisher=Yale University Press|isbn=9780300187847|page=129|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eaL0AgAAQBAJ&q=Blaise+Hamlet+William+Gilpin&pg=PA129|access-date=2021-01-01|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701051402/https://books.google.com/books?id=eaL0AgAAQBAJ&q=Blaise+Hamlet+William+Gilpin&pg=PA129}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Southworth|first1=Michael|last2=Ben-Joseph|first2=Eran|title=Streets and the Shaping of Towns and Cities|date=2013|publisher=Island Press|isbn=9781610911092|pages=29–31|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UQvGNKBfCgsC&q=Blaise+Hamlet&pg=PA30|access-date=2021-01-01|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701052513/https://books.google.com/books?id=UQvGNKBfCgsC&q=Blaise+Hamlet&pg=PA30}}</ref> 一条椭圆形的小路将小屋连接在一起，环绕着村庄绿地及[[日晷|日晷]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Blaise Hamlet, Bristol, England - Description|url=http://www.parksandgardens.org/places-and-people/site/444/description|website=Parks and Gardens UK|publisher=Parks and Gardens Data Services Ltd|access-date=8 August 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810205629/http://www.parksandgardens.org/places-and-people/site/444/description|archive-date=10 August 2016}}</ref> 小屋花园为[[维多利亚时代|维多利亚时代]]风格。<ref>{{cite web|title=Blaise Hamlet, Bristol, England - History|url=http://www.parksandgardens.org/places-and-people/site/444/history|website=Parks and Gardens UK|publisher=Parks and Gardens Data Services Ltd|access-date=8 August 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810220217/http://www.parksandgardens.org/places-and-people/site/444/history|archive-date=10 August 2016}}</ref>。

自1943年以来，这些小屋一直归国家信托所有<ref name=nthist/>。玫瑰小屋作为度假小屋。它们不向公众开放，但可以从绿地欣赏。

